text: Anastasija Tarasova (born 1 September 1998) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a forward for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club Liepājas Futbola skola. She has been a member of the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers
